reviews.reviewText: This is a fantastic alcohol-free mouthwash that tastes so natural and refreshes your breath wonderfully unless you have some sort of hygiene problem, however my personal experience it works really great

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 8, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars The most pleasant mouthwash ever
reviews.reviewText: I'm not a big fan of the harsher mouthwashes, but after using this, my mouth does feel fresh, particularly when I use it before I go out the door in the morning after the usual tooth brushing routines. This product doesn't sting or make my eyes tear up, it has a pleasant lingering sense of fresh breath, and helps me feel good about maintaining a "keto" eating lifestyle. I recommend this to anyone who doesn't like the usual unpleasantness of regular mouthwash, whether or not you are eating a special diet where "keto" breath might be your concern. It may be a bit more expensive than the standard OTC mouth wash, but I seldom use the other stuff because it is so stringent and harsh; this is very fresh feeling without harshness.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 30, 2022
reviews.reviewText: what I like about the product:- better ingredients than other mouthwash on the market- very minty wintergreen flavor (will leave your breath minty fresh!) .. if you don't like it very minty, you could probably water it down- a little goes a long way!- mouth feels clean and fresh after usedislike:- claims to be all natural, but contains some ingredients I cant pronounce such as: 1,3-propanediol , and a few others too long to type...- you cant really gargle because it creates too much bubbles
